		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hard-wired palettes can be effective, but if not done carefully will be very obvious (like in the Zelda games). I had no idea that the Battle Toads games did this, so they must have executed very well <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" />

		

		</td>
