	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Note that many modern HDTVs cannot handle 240p well, and will turn anything that flickers into a mess of alternating scanlines. An effect like this would likely look very bad.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


